public static final class StatementSet.Builder extends com.google.protobuf.GeneratedMessageV3.Builder<StatementSet.Builder> implements StatementSetOrBuilder
 The StatementSet represents a list of statements or "tree nodes," each of which follow the same
 behavior as the Statement proto message.
